    "causal_summary": "The v1.0.2 stress-test rerun closed with four follow-ups tagged in `../010-stress-test-rerun-v1-0-2/findings.md` Recommendations §1-5 — three concrete P0/P1/P2 bugs and one telemetry-leverage opportunity. Each is currently \"tagged for follow-up\" but lacks a refined fix proposal: the right intervention point, alternatives considered, falsifiable success criteria, and a recommended scope estimate for the eventual remediation packet. Without that refinement step, the follow-ups stay open indefinitely or get scoped poorly downstream.",
